In the MATTER OF BEATRICE R.H., Respondent. Dean E.H., Appellant;
v.
Penny F.H., Non-Party Respondent. (A.D. No. 2014-10563) Court of Appeals of New York. February 8, 2018

Appeal dismissed without costs, by the Court, sua sponte, upon the ground that the order appealed from does not finally *1243**853determine the proceeding within the meaning of the Constitution.
